Package: cedar
Type: Package
Title: Cost-Effectiveness Decision Analysis in R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-11-09
Authors@R: person("Jefferson", "McMillan-Wilhoit",
                  email = "jmcmil13@jhu.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jefferson McMillan-Wilhoit <jmcmil13@jhu.edu>
Description: Provides tools and functions for conducting cost-effectiveness
    analysis (CEA). This package supports decision-analytic modeling,
    probabilistic sensitivity analysis, and value of information calculations
    commonly used in health economics and policy evaluation.
